A fire has broken out at Tony’s Colour Automotive Paints, on the corner of Orphirton and Fraser Street in Booysens.
Firefighters and emergency personnel are making their way to the scene.
ALSO READ: Factory fire in Kempton Park damages neighbouring buildings
It is not yet clear what caused the fire, but no fatalities have been reported.




This is a developing story. Updates to follow as more information becomes available.
